{"tid":1078271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登人支唔支持三隧分流","createTime":"2019-03-26T07:25:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T08:33:37.000Z","uid":64634,"like":16,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f02280e76a0fa06fe839ea456964cfa8c98f2ee7","tid":1078271,"uid":64634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:25:05.000Z","msg":"坦白講，依家立法會唔夠票過三隧分流，民建聯已經成為最大反對黨，值得宣揚開去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港渣車嘅人得八十萬...成個立法會，無論泛民建制都為左80萬人利益而忽略更大既公眾利益......<br />\n<br />\n政府仲要承諾用啲錢黎plan congestion pricing等等 ，呢啲政策都可以令渣私家車成本增加而減少渣車，搭巴士既人就可以享受一條無咁塞車嘅路......<br />\n<br />\n雖然廣大市民係既得利益者，但係都因為未必直接感受到得益而唔會大聲叫支持，相反揸車嘅人就好明顯知道政策對佢哋嘅損害，反對都大聲啲⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n所以做下民調先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持三隧分流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5192c89296c1f01fc811c55f018fde8a96c3e5d4","tid":1078271,"uid":64634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:30:57.000Z","msg":"大家支持反對討論下"},{"pid":"dd6a2d00b21f76d8bf2705a481fb28c43e2db7d2","tid":1078271,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:41:33.000Z","msg":"政府推嘅一定反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9d6cece8be45783264db2e9eab1ab7339583e3","tid":1078271,"uid":64634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd6a2d00b21f76d8bf2705a481fb28c43e2db7d2","tid":1078271,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:41:33.000Z","msg":"政府推嘅一定反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:42:40.000Z","msg":"建制反對既話你會唔會支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img